data.description: One of a kind, majestic stone front colonial offering over 4800 sq ft, 5 spacious bedrooms, 3.5 baths tucked in a quiet cul-de-sac in the Highspire development and desirable Council Rock school district. The exterior provides beautifully landscaped yard, circular driveway, in-ground pool that was recently re-tiled and plastered and 12 zone sprinkler system for the front yard.  The first floor offers formal living and dining room, library/office, media room, laundry room, expansive  kitchen with  large center island with cook top, breakfast room, spacious family room with floor to ceiling marble wood fireplace with wet bar and front & back staircases. 2nd floor boasts primary suite with sitting room and tons of closet space.  Primary bathroom features Jacuzzi tub, stall shower and double sink vanity. There are 4 additional generous size bedrooms. one with private bathroom.  There's also a large hall bath with tub shower and double sink vanity.  This home has a 400A elect service, perfect for charging of electric vehicles.  Home also features 3 car side entry garage,  private backyard with stone patio, massive unfinished basement and whole house generator. With your personal touches, this can be your dream home!
